creator: Webtel Electrosoft Pvt. Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
Web-EDGE for a modern organization, the accomplishment of any Task management activity relates to the tools they utilize.

Using Web-Edge, you figure out the correct potential of your staff and accordingly Quote your agreeable and chargeable rates for Each Assignment, resulting in growth of your organization and profitability.

Silent Features
+ Comprehensive Office Management Tool.

+ Manage Assignments – Allocate – Update – Review from Anywhere.

+ Prioritize Jobs – Set due dates

+ Automated Alerts for Overdue, Completed or Ready to be invoiced jobs.

+ Inbuilt Statutory Compliance Tracker.

+ Invoice generation for Completed Assignments to speed up recovery.

+ Import Invoices into Tally. No need for re-entry.

+ Calculation of Work-in-progress at end of any period for analysis.

+ User Management – Maker Checker – Job Tracking/Approval system.

+ Management Dashboard for Effective Control.

+ Attendance/Time sheet for better Productivity of employees.

+ Assessment of Assignment wise Man hour cost.

+ Ready made Checklists for staff with facility to update or create new ones.

+ Efficient & Effective Document Management System

+ Appointment Tracker for Effective Time Management.

+ Performance based Review of Employees.

+ E-diary of Articled Assistants as required by ICAI.

+ Bulk Import of Masters.

+ Multiple Reports for Review and Analysis.

Using Web-Edge, you figure out the correct potential of your staff and accordingly Quote your agreeable and chargeable rates for Each Assignment, resulting in growth of your organization and profitability.

Silent Features
+ Comprehensive Office Management Tool.

+ Manage Assignments – Allocate – Update – Review from Anywhere.

+ Prioritize Jobs – Set due dates

+ Automated Alerts for Overdue, Completed or Ready to be invoiced jobs.

+ Inbuilt Statutory Compliance Tracker.

+ Invoice generation for Completed Assignments to speed up recovery.

+ Import Invoices into Tally. No need for re-entry.

+ Calculation of Work-in-progress at end of any period for analysis.

+ User Management – Maker Checker – Job Tracking/Approval system.

+ Management Dashboard for Effective Control.

+ Attendance/Time sheet for better Productivity of employees.

+ Assessment of Assignment wise Man hour cost.

+ Ready made Checklists for staff with facility to update or create new ones.

+ Efficient & Effective Document Management System

+ Appointment Tracker for Effective Time Management.

+ Performance based Review of Employees.

+ E-diary of Articled Assistants as required by ICAI.

+ Bulk Import of Masters.

+ Multiple Reports for Review and Analysis.
descriptionShort: Employer's directions for growth and efficiency
